properties.name: NO_PREFIX_SUFFIX
properties.description: Does not use a prefix or suffix.

properties.name: PREFIX_SUFFIX_REFERENCE
properties.description: Places the prefix and/or suffix on the footnote reference number in the main text.

properties.name: PREFIX_SUFFIX_MARKER
properties.description: Places the prefix and/or suffix on the footnote marker number in the footnote text.

properties.name: PREFIX_SUFFIX_BOTH
properties.description: Places the prefix and/or suffix on both the the footnote reference number in the main text and the footnote marker number in the footnote text.

name: FootnotePrefixSuffix
description: Footnote prefix or suffix placement options.
